      <title>国际货币基金组织敦促日本央行为加息做好准备，以防通胀加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/imf-urges-boj-to-prepare-for-rate-hike-in-case-inflation-flares</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织表示，日本央行需要做好加息准备，以防通胀意外加剧，但目前其宽松政策立场仍然适当。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/imf-urges-boj-to-prepare-for-rate-hike-in-case-inflation-flares</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 13:00:08 GMT</pubDate>
