    <item>
      <title>兰博基尼订单满载，超级富豪继续购物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/lamborghini-sees-full-order-books-as-super-rich-keep-shopping</link>
      <description><![CDATA[兰博基尼的超级跑车在 2026 年之前就已售罄，因为最富有的消费者几乎没有受到全球经济放缓影响的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/lamborghini-sees-full-order-books-as-super-rich-keep-shopping</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织大幅下调阿根廷 Milei 政策增长预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/imf-sharply-cuts-argentina-s-growth-forecast-on-milei-s-policies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织下调了对阿根廷的增长预期，预测南美洲第二大经济体将连续两年萎缩，因为总统哈维尔·米莱推动“重大政策调整”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/imf-sharply-cuts-argentina-s-growth-forecast-on-milei-s-policies</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织警告英国不要在即将到来的预算中减税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/don-t-cut-taxes-at-march-budget-imf-tells-uk-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织表示，英国政府不应在预算中减税，因为它需要资金投资公共服务并控制国家债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/don-t-cut-taxes-at-march-budget-imf-tells-uk-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通用汽车超出第四季度预期，预计 2024 年利润和销售额将增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-30/gm-tops-4q-estimates-sees-2024-profit-sales-growing-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[通用汽车公司预计，在第四季度超出华尔街预期后，由于美国销量的改善，今年利润将增长。克雷格·特鲁德尔在彭博电视台进行报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-01-30/gm-tops-4q-estimates-sees-2024-profit-sales-growing-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 12:56:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
