      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 09:02:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管做出绿色承诺，印度电力巨头仍需要更多煤炭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/top-indian-power-utility-eyes-9-6-billion-of-renewable-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最大的电力生产商NTPC Ltd.尽管承诺投资数十亿美元用于绿色能源，但仍在提高其燃煤发电能力，凸显了该国在平衡能源安全和实现气候目标方面面临的困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/top-indian-power-utility-eyes-9-6-billion-of-renewable-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 07:53:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
